" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2640629789347426%26id%3D124616407615456&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F%2Fkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=6997dd7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456</a><br />\n<br />\nPost：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eDEkrT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eDEkrT</a><br />\n<br />\n//平等機會婦女聯席發言人區美寶稱，3個組織11月初共同發起控訴警察性暴力的國際聯署，截至本月7日收集到21國共85個團體聯署支持。為了向聯合國專家展開更有力游說，3個組織呼籲受害者主動聯絡他們並接受訪談，強調會保密。//<br />\n<br />\n我們現正收集抗爭者在抗爭期間／被捕後遭受警察性暴力對待的資料，作以下用途：<br />\n1. 協助受害人可以完整保留該事件之紀錄<br />\n2. 整理資料並製成 #ProtestToo 實錄，以作追究之用<br />\n3. 收集國際聯署（進行中），結合個案提交聯合國，爭取國際間關注及支持<br />\n4. 要求香港政府獨立、公正地徹查「反送中運動」發生的性暴力<br />\n<br />\n*個人資料及通訊紀錄在實錄完成後可按受訪者意願全部銷毀<br />\n詳情及相關安排請聯絡Tg @protesttoo"},{"pid":"448ad18e8836252cbf403951991b226c57b14642","tid":1776353,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"678f6e1919b7c987d040f9020fc2a42192003a34","tid":1776353,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"72bc2e5d089264f04bf563d80ff960eeee5a0839","tid":1776353,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ccfdf0295c121e0f17024192e3a58623395b565","tid":1776353,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:14:35.000Z","msg":"死乞衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:16:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:19:49.000Z","msg":"成舊水打一次J我都比唔起.."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:24:01.000Z","msg":"咁你就米鬧人死乞衣la"},{"pid":"9cd4ce8a9a788962be4801fab309072f88c83941","tid":1776353,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"448ad18e8836252cbf403951991b226c57b14642","tid":1776353,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike"